{ [Yuriy's corner]The following 5 games were solely annotated by Yuriy, who's succesfully played the Grünfeld in many critical games en-route to the IM title.    My hope is that you find them instructive and entertaining, I certainly did! }1. --
*
[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
