{ [Key middlegame themes and pawn structures]This chapter illustrates a number of key middlegame and endgame themes that occur time and time again in the Grünfeld.    Understanding the strategic concepts outlined in this chapter will assist you in absorbing the material in the theoretical chapters and help you make better decisions in practical games. It is my hope that it will also improve your general chess understanding! }1. --
