3. d5{ is the most combative and dynamic response to the fianchetto system. Black goes for ... d5  right away in true Grunfeld style! }( 3...c6 { with the idea  d5  to erect a Slav structure is fully playable but not at all exciting. White has a myriad of move orders and setups, not to mention the option of taking on  d5  and going for a symmetric position where only the first player can ever be better. } )
