13. e3
13. Ne5{ Black followed up with ... Nbc6  and had an excellent position out of the opening in 1-0 (38) Svidler,P  (2749) -Grischuk,A (2763) Astana 2012. White did win this high profile game, but it had nothing to do with the current position. In fact, Black was better for the vast majority of it, only blundering much later on. }
