14. Nc5{ White pre-emptively covered the  c2  square only to run into another neat knight jump. White experienced a true 'knightmare' in the game ½-½ }{ (74) }{ Wojtaszek,R }{ (2701) }{ -Tomczak,J }{ (2565) }{ Poland 2013! }
{ The tactical justification behind Black's last move is now illustrated: }15. dxc5
