10. dxc5{ Having fallen so far behind in development, White accepts there's really no way to hold onto the center and instead seeks to exchange queens in an attempt to hold back Black's active play. }( 10.Be3 { desperately trying to hold onto the center runs into }10...Ng4 11.Rd1 b4! { when things have obviously gone wrong for White. } )
