3. d5{ is the most combative and dynamic response to the fianchetto system. Black goes for ... d5  right away in true Grünfeld style! }
4. Bg2{ is more flexible than  Nf3 . White's bishop surely belongs on  g2  while the  g1  knight may choose to come out to  e2 . }
