13. Rb8{ improves over the game 0-1 (42) Petakov,U (2366) -Tadic,B (2495) Palic 2014, where Black went for the hasty ... Qxd4 . The  d4  isn't running anywhere and Black does best in targeting the  b2  pawn first. }
